'''No Tears For Ananse''' ni filime yo muri [[Gana]] yayobowe na Sam Aryeetey kandi yanditswe na Ato Kwamina Yanney mu 1968.   

== Umugambi ==
Filime ya rubanda isobanura uburyo amayeri Ananse agerageza kurenza umuryango we kubera igitutu cyo guha umuryango we burimunsi. Yigize nk'uwapfuye abwira umuryango we kumushyingura mu isambu ye, bityo aribwa n'abakozi bashinzwe ibiryo mu murima igihe cyatinze. Umuryango washyizeho umutego ukoresheje igishusho cyometseho kole. Ananse abonye igishusho atekereza ko ari kizima nuko atangira  no gukubitaho urushyi arumirwa. Bukeye bwaho, yafashwe n'umuryango ndetse n'abaturage. 

